Text: Can someone tell me the difference between clicking "DOWNLOAD THIS TORRENT" and "MAGNET LINK"?
Does anyone know where i can get the 720p of this episode
Yeah one you click on and the other you do not

When you click on "Download this torrent" a popup comes up asking what to do with the file, you usually then click open with utorrent and dowload the file. But when you click "Magnet Link" it automatically adds the torrent on utorrent for download. 

Hope i explained ok.
HEY thanks for taking the time to explain. But WHY bother if thats the only difference? Is there no more to it than that?
Why is there no 720p up for this episode yet?
